file.name: DelinquentAccountHandling.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Delinquent Account Handling
  description: This service domain handles delinquent accounts (typically for active credit/charge cards) for follow-up of payments due through periodic review and contacts. This process ends when the account is cancelled and is transferred to Collections
  contact:
    name: BIAN
    url: https://bian.org
  version: 11.0.0
servers:
  - url: https://virtserver.swaggerhub.com/BIAN-3/BIAN/DelinquentAccountHandling/11.0.0
paths:
  /DelinquentAccountHandling/Initiate:

      tags:
        - CR - DelinquentAccountProcedure
      summary: InCR Initiate delinquent account processing
      description: InCR Initiate delinquent account processing
      operationId: Initiate
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/InitiateDelinquentAccountProcedureRequest'
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/InitiateDelinquentAccountProcedureResponse'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '403':

        '404':

        '500':

  '/DelinquentAccountHandling/{delinquentaccounthandlingid}/Update':

        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '403':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Forbidden'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
        '429':

        '500':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/InternalServerError'
  '/DelinquentAccountHandling/{delinquentaccounthandlingid}/Retrieve':
    get:
      tags:
        - CR - DelinquentAccountProcedure
      summary: ReCR Retrieve details about a delinquent account procedure
      description: ReCR Retrieve details about a delinquent account procedure
      operationId: Retrieve
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/delinquentaccounthandlingid'

      summary: ReBQ Retrieve details about a delinquent account assessment

      operationId: RetrieveAssessment

    HTTPError:

          format: string

      type: object
      properties:

          format: string

    Contact:

        ContactResult:

        DocumentDirectoryEntryInstanceReference:

          format: object
        DocumentContent:

          format: string
        CorrespondenceInstanceReference:

          format: string
        DelinquentAccountContactResult:
          type: string
          description: The result of the tracking and reminder activity
          format: string
        DelinquentAccountContactWorkProduct:
          type: string
          description: 'Work documentation, forms and schedules produced and referenced during the task'
          format: string
      description: "The main worsteps to be followed in th eexecution of the procedure\n\nExamples: Invoice generation"
    Payment:
      type: object
      properties:
        PaymentTransactionReference:
          type: string
          description: Reference to the received payment
          format: object
        PaymentTransaction:
          type: string
          description: Payment transaction details
          format: string
      description: "The main worsteps to be followed in th eexecution of the procedure\n\nExamples: Invoice generation"
    Resolution:
      type: object
      properties:
        DelinquentAccountResolutionTaskResult:
          type: string
          description: 'The result of the resolution planning activity (e.g.. account recovered, passed to collections)'
          format: string
        DelinquentAccountResolutionActionPlan:
          type: string
          description: The recommended processing for the delinquent account - details passed on to associated function for execution as necessary
          format: string
        DelinquentAccountResolutionWorkProduct:
          type: string
          description: 'Work documentation, forms and schedules produced and referenced during the task'
          format: string
      description: "The main worsteps to be followed in th eexecution of the procedure\n\nExamples: Invoice generation"
    currencycode:
      type: object
      properties:
        Currencycode:
          type: string
          description: "A code identifying a currency according to ISO-4217.\nA currency is a system of money in general use in a particular country.\n\nCode allocated to a currency, by a maintenance agency, under an international identification scheme as described in the latest edition of the international standard ISO 4217 \"Codes for the representation of currencies and funds\". Valid currency codes are registered with the ISO 4217 Maintenance Agency, and consist of three contiguous letters. (ISO20022)\n\n"
          format: datatype
      description: The primary account currency
    DelinquentAccountProcedure:
      type: object
      properties:
        ProductInstanceReference:
          type: string
          description: The linked credit product reference
          format: object
        ProductAccountNumber:
          type: string
          description: The associated account number in any suitable format (e.g. IBAN)
          format: string
        ProductandServiceType:
          type: string
          description: The type of product
          format: string
        CustomerReference:

          format: object
        BankBranchLocationReference:

          description: Bank branch associated with the account for booking purposes
          format: object
        IssuedDevice:

          format: string
        AccountCurrency:

        Associations:

        AssociationType:

          format: string
        AssociationObligationEntitlement:

        AssociationReference:

          format: object

        LinkType:

          format: string
        PositionLimits:

        PaymentTransactions:

        DelinquentAccountProcessingSchedule:

          description: Details the schedule of actions to be applied to the delinquent account

      description: 'Complete work tasks following a defined procedure in support of general office activities and product and service delivery within Delinquent Account Handling. '
